### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@authToken = dummy-token-for-testing

### Récupérer tous les projets
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json

### Récupérer les projets publiés
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?isPublished=true
Content-Type: application/json

### Récupérer les projets par catégorie
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?category=WEBSITE
Content-Type: application/json

### Créer un nouveau projet
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Portfolio Website",
  "description": "A responsive portfolio website for a designer",
  "category": "WEBSITE",
  "thumbnail": "/uploads/portfolio-thumb.jpg",
  "images": "[\"uploads/portfolio1.jpg\", \"uploads/portfolio2.jpg\"]",
  "year": 2023,
  "client": "John Doe",
  "duration": "2 months",
  "industry": "Design",
  "scope": "[\"UI/UX\", \"Development\", \"Deployment\"]",
  "challenge": "Creating a unique design that stands out",
  "approach": "Used modern web technologies and minimalist design",
  "isPublished": true
}

### Récupérer un projet par ID (remplacer l'ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/project-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

### Mettre à jour un projet (remplacer l'ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/project-id-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Updated Portfolio Website",
  "description": "A responsive portfolio website for a designer with updated features",
  "category": "WEBSITE",
  "thumbnail": "/uploads/portfolio-thumb.jpg",
  "images": "[\"uploads/portfolio1.jpg\", \"uploads/portfolio2.jpg\", \"uploads/portfolio3.jpg\"]",
  "year": 2023,
  "client": "John Doe",
  "duration": "3 months",
  "industry": "Design",
  "scope": "[\"UI/UX\", \"Development\", \"Deployment\", \"SEO\"]",
  "challenge": "Creating a unique design that stands out",
  "approach": "Used modern web technologies and minimalist design",
  "isPublished": true
}

### Publier/dépublier un projet (remplacer l'ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/project-id-here/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "isPublished": false
}

### Réorganiser les projets
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "projectOrders": [
    { "id": "project-id-1", "order": 0 },
    { "id": "project-id-2", "order": 1 },
    { "id": "project-id-3", "order": 2 }
  ]
}

### Dupliquer un projet (remplacer l'ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/project-id-here/duplicate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Supprimer un projet (remplacer l'ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/project-id-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}